# scuzzie

simple static webcomic site generator

## installation

basic (cli) version:

```shell
$ pip install scuzzie
$ scuzzie --help
```

with tk gui:

```shell
$ pip install scuzzie[gui]
$ scuzzie-gui
```

you'll need a python built with tcl-tk support for the gui to work.

